cription":"John Wycliffe, English theologian and professor at the University of Oxford, completed a translation of the Bible from the Latin Vulgate into Middle English. This translation is known as Wycliffe's Bible and was completed around 1382.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Sir Thomas John Bigge was born in 1378, in Marden, Kent, England as the son of Biggs and Gese von Negendank. He married Gese von Negendank before 1395, in England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. He died in 1452, in his hometown, at the age of 74."},"et":{"1378–1452":"1378–1452","–Female":"Surnud","1380–1430":"1380–1430","1395–1474":"1395–1474","1406–1443":"1406–1443","1350–Male":"1350–Surnud","1378":"1378","1443":"1443","1430":"1430","1452":"1452","1474":"1474","before 1395":"enne 1395","1395":"1395","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1380":"1380","1406":"1406","Marden, Kent, England":"Marden, Kent, England","Benenden, Kent, England":"Benenden, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Crotehill, Benenden, Kent, England":"Benenden, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1378–1452":"1378–1452","–Female":"Kuollut","1380–1430":"1380–1430","1395–1474":"1395–1474","1406–1443":"1406–1443","1350–Male":"1350–Kuollut","1378":"1378","1443":"1443","1430":"1430","1452":"1452","1474":"1474","before 1395":"ennen vuotta 1395","1395":"1395","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1380":"1380","1406":"1406","Marden, Kent, England":"Marden, Kent, England","Benenden, Kent, England":"Benenden, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Crotehill, Benenden, Kent, England":"Benenden, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1378–1452":"1378–1452","–Female":"Décédée","1380–1430":"1380–1430","1395–1474":"1395–1474","1406–1443":"1406–1443","1350–Male":"1350–Décédé","1378":"1378","1443"